This is my first try at making an AWP map. In the development I wanted to make a original map. Which turned out to be a simple yet awesome map ^^ I've learnt a couple of new stuff. Things included in the map:

AWP_FLOAT

The map includes the following: - Models (diffrent on both sides, to create variations) - Fog - Displacements - 18 spawn points for both, Terrorists and Counter Terrorists. - Ladder - HDR - dustmotes - cubemaps - light/spotlights I hope you will try it out and maybe add it to a server ^^ if you do please let me know. I may make this into a gg_map as well ^^ I may do that later if some of you guys want it. I also made a video of the map, check it out! I used source recorder to record it then demo smoother to make the nice smooth effect to it ^^ It was my first time trying out the demo smoother, so it's a bit buggy ^^ I also mixed the video with the music in some places. enjoy!

This is the awp version of de_favela_rio.

Terrorists spawn in various balconies and roofs in the higher part of the favela, whilst CTs spawn in the low part of the favela. HE grenades are also available. The roofs are assessible by the exposed pipes on the walls which can be climbed.

It offers a very unique and non conventional gameplay. Players must know and be always aware of the ennemies sniper spots.

A nav file included in bsp. Playing with bots is also quite fun in this map.

Have fun, and give me your feedback.

This is the 2nd version of my awp map. It has drastically changed for the better. There are more things to do.

Check out the screenshots.

EDIT: After more testing it has been found that the left side teleport on the CT side is flawed and the player gets stuck in the wall. This will be a fix in v3 that comes out some time within the next 3 days.

Bugs found in v2:

Flawed teleport
Water too shallow
Too bright
Walls on 2nd level buildings can be shot through
Very tough to jump over top and down onto battlefield area

Some things missing that will be in v3:

trigger_push where the long straight walkways are so it goes quicker and you dont get shot

Deeper water so you dont get health deducted when you fall

A more intricately designed bunker in the middle

Fix up the awp arena so that there are places you can stand up and still be protected.

Doors so you can exit the spawn area into the middle, yet you cant enter back in.

Teleports that bring you back into your own spawn if you so desire.

Some secrets

Fix bugs



The giant platform in the middle IS breakable. by the way
